<p>The ATHM # references the accession number given to collections by the American Textile History Museum (ATHM). These numbers have been kept and tracked for researchers looking for former citations. The ATHM accession number for this collection was 0022.143.</p>  </processinfo>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_94c6aef3650e80b374dee46d02d0ed7d">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>Includes account book of Nesmith &amp; Tatterson, 1845-1849, listing goods delivered, including raw materials and dyestuffs, as well as goods sent elsewhere for finishing. Also includes ledger, 1845-1851, of payroll and manufacturing accounts; a work and time book, 1845-1848; a weave room time book, 1851-1852, listing workers' names; and weaving records, 1849-1850, listing workers' names, number of pieces, weight, and number of yards.</p>  </scopecontent>
